<a name="biography" id="biography"></a>
<div id="artist-biography" style="padding-left:10px;margin:0;border-left: solid 5px #f0f0f0;">

<strong>The Contortionist biography</strong><br />
The Contortionist is an American progressive metal band from Indianapolis, Indiana. <br><br>Formed in 2007, the band released a couple of EPs before releasing their debut full-length studio album "Exoplanet" in 2010.<br><br>Tthe band consists of guitarists Robby Baca and Cameron Maynard, drummer Joey Baca, vocalist Mike Lessard, bassist Jordan Eberhardt, and keyboardist Eric Guenther. <br><br>They have released four studio albums and three EPs. The band signed with eOne Music and Good Fight Entertainment in early 2010. The musicians draw from influences as diverse as Meshuggah, Dream Theater, Isis, Rush, Cynic and Pat Metheny.



